# General Rules

- First script, then template tags. Not style tags.
- Use functional javascript
- Keep things modular by creating new components when it makes sense. Follow the Dont Repeat Yourself (DRY) principle.

# UI

- Use nuxt-ui components when ever possible
- TailwindCSS for styling
- Keep a mobile first design philosophy




